---
title: Mumbai Chicken & Carrot Ribbon Slaw with Mint
description: Carrot ribbons are a heavenly alternative to heavy noodles. With a little help from Mumbai spices, tender chicken and fragrant mint, you'll feel like you're floating on a delicious cloud.

